        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 3. A–B, Amphiporus lactifloreus (Johnston, 1828) (ICHUM 3280); A, anaesthetized living specimen; B, transverse section showing vascular plug (arrowhead); C–E, Quasitetrastemma stimpsoni (Chernyshev, 1992) (C, D, unregistered specimen, 3 July 2004, Akkeshi; E, ICHUM 5972); C, dorsal surface at anterior end, anaesthetized living specimen; D, ventral surface at anterior end, anaesthetized living specimen; E, transverse section showing vascular plug (arrowhead). Scale bars: 2 mm (A); 50 µm (B, E); no scales for C, D." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4475134/files/figure.png" .

